ing%20parliamentary%20sessions%20and%20committee%20meetings%2C%20MPs%20are%20entitled%20to%20a%20daily%20allowance%20of%20%E2%82%B92%2C000%20to%20cover%20lodging%2C%20food%20and%20any%20other%20expenses%20while%20they%20are%20in%20the%20capital.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ETravel%20allowance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20are%20entitled%20to%2034%20free%20domestic%20air%20journeys%20per%20year%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20immediate%20families.%20They%20also%20receive%20free%20first-class%20train%20travel%20for%20official%20and%20personal%20purposes.%20MPs%20can%20also%20claim%20mileage%20allowances%20when%20travelling%20by%20road%20within%20their%20constituencies.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHousing%20and%20accommodation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20are%20given%20rent-free%20accommodations%20in%20prime%20areas%20during%20their%205-year%20term.%20Depending%20on%20seniority%2C%20they%20may%20receive%20bungalows%2C%20flats%20or%20hostel%20rooms.%20Those%20who%20choose%20not%20to%20use%20the%20official%20accommodation%20can%20claim%20a%20housing%20allowance%20of%20%E2%82%B92%2C00%2C000%20per%20month.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EMedical%20facilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20and%20their%20immediate%20families%20are%20entitled%20to%20free%20medical%20care%20under%20the%20Central%20Government%20Health%20Scheme%20(CGHS).%20This%20includes%20treatment%20at%20government%20hospitals%20and%20select%20private%20hospitals%20which%20come%20under%20the%20scheme.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPension%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFormer%20MPs%20receive%20a%20pension%20of%20%E2%82%B925%2C000%20per%20month%20after%20serving%20one%20term%20in%20Parliament.%20For%20every%20extra%20year%20of%20service%2C%20they%20get%20an%20increment%20of%20%E2%82%B92%2C000%20per%20month.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPhone%20and%20internet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20are%20allotted%20up%20to%201%2C50%2C000%20free%20telephone%20calls%20annually.%20They%20also%20receive%20free%20high-speed%20internet%20connections%20at%20their%20residences%20and%20offices.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWater%20and%20electricity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20are%20provided%20with%20free%20electricity%20up%20to%2050%2C000%20units%20and%20free%20water%20up%20to%204%2C000%20kilolitres%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717732500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fum6j1rso_new-parliament-building_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-all-about-salaries-perks-of-members-of-parliament-5831798%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MPs%20are%20given%20rent-free%20accommodations%20in%20prime%20areas%20during%20their%205-year%20term.%20Depending%20on%20seniority%2C%20they%20may%20receive%20bungalows%2C%20flats%20or%20hostel%20rooms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-all-about-salaries-perks-of-members-of-parliament-5831798%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-all-about-salaries-perks-of-members-of-parliament-5831798%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-all-about-salaries-perks-of-members-of-parliament-5831798%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Congress'%20Stock%20Market%20Charge%2C%20BJP's%20%26quot%3B5th%20Largest%20Economy%26quot%3B%20Rebuttal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20Thursday%20hit%20back%20at%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20who%20had%20alleged%20a%20connection%20between%20%26quot%3BBJP%2C%20exit%20pollsters%20and%20dubious%20foreign%20investors%26quot%3B.%20It%20also%20accused%20the%20Congress%20leader%20of%20%26quot%3Bconspiring%20to%20mislead%20market%20investors%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Union%20Commerce%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20leader%20%26quot%3Bhas%20still%20not%20overcome%20the%20opposition's%20defeat%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Several%20opposition%20parties%20had%20come%20together%20to%20form%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20had%20alleged%20that%20there%20was%20a%20loss%20of%20lakhs%20of%20crores%20to%20retail%20investors%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bfake%20exit%20polls%26quot%3B%20and%20demanded%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20probe%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20stock%20market%20scam.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20said%20in%20the%20past%2019%20years%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20government%2C%20the%20market%20capitalization%20of%20Indian%20stocks%20crossed%20%245%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20has%20still%20not%20overcome%20the%20loss%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections.%20Now%2C%20he%20is%20conspiring%20to%20mislead%20the%20market%20investors.%20Today%2C%20India%20has%20become%20the%20fifth-largest%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20minister%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20wants%20to%20instil%20%26quot%3Bfear%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20both%20the%20domestic%20and%20global%20investors%2C%20so%20that%20they%20do%20not%20invest%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20know%20equity%20markets%20react%20to%20various%20estimates%20and%20predictions%20during%20any%20elections%2C%20or%20for%20that%20matter%20any%20forecasts%20by%20banks%20and%20institutions.%20Ups%20and%20downs%20are%20normal%20even%20during%20a%20non-event%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20this%20year%2C%20market%20caps%20of%20both%20BSE%20and%20NSE-listed%20companies%20touched%20%245%20trillion.%20Market%20capitalisation%20or%20market%20cap%20is%20the%20total%20value%20of%20a%20company's%20stock%2C%20derived%20at%20by%20multiplying%20the%20stock%20price%20by%20the%20number%20of%20its%20outstanding%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20stocks%20market%20entered%20the%20league%20of%20top%20five%20stock%20markets%20globally%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20m-cap%20of%20PSU%20companies%20has%20risen%20four-fold%20over%20the%20past%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20investors%2C%20particularly%20the%20retail%20investors%2C%20have%20benefitted%20from%20the%20rise%20in%20stock%20indices%20over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRetail%20investors%20are%20not%20just%20bystanders%20today%2C%20but%20are%20participating%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFPI%20holdings%20in%20India%20were%2021%20per%20cent%20during%20UPA%20days%20and%20it%20has%20dipped%20to%20now%2016%20per%20cent%2C%20he%20said.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Indians%20investing%20in%20stock%20markets%20have%20gone%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20considered%20a%20well-regulated%20market%2C%20and%20SEBI%20has%20received%20several%20appreciations%20worldwide%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India%20was%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bamong%20fragile%205%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20and%20that%20the%20country%20was%20now%20the%20fifth%20biggest%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20Fragile%205%20was%20coined%20by%20a%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analyst%20in%202013%2C%20which%20referred%20to%20a%20set%20of%20five%20emerging%20countries%2C%20including%20India%2C%20whose%20economy%20was%20not%20doing%20well%20back%20then.%20The%20other%20four%20countries%20were%20Brazil%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20size%20of%20the%20mutual%20fund%20industry%20was%20only%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20crore%20in%202014%2C%20today%20it%20has%20increased%20more%20than%205%20times%20to%20Rs%2056%20lakh%20crore.%20Through%20mutual%20funds%2C%20Indian%20investors%20especially%20small%20investors%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20this%20growing%20market%20today%20and%20these%20small%20retail%20investors%20have%20ensured%20that%20India's%20ownership%20today%20has%20instantly%20become%20more%20than%20the%20ownership%20of%20institutional%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20April%20and%20May%2C%20when%20the%20market%20was%20rising%2C%20foreigners%20sold%20in%20the%20market%20and%20Indian%20investors%20took%20advantage%20of%20it%20and%20bought%20it.%20The%20benefit%20of%20this%20rise%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months%20has%20been%20received%20by%20Indian%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20latest%20outflows%20by%20foreign%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20and%20May%2C%20FPIs%20were%20net%20sellers%20in%20Indian%20stock%20markets%2C%20data%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20results%20came%20on%20June%204%2C%20when%20the%20market%20fell%2C%20foreign%20investors%20sold%20at%20a%20low%20price%20and%20Indian%20investors%20bought%20it%20with%20the%20belief%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20coming%20and%20we%20would%20take%20advantage%20of%20it.%20So%20foreigners%20bought%20at%20a%20high%20price%20and%20sold%20at%20a%20low%20price.%20Indian%20investors%20sold%20at%20a%20high%20price%20and%20bought%20at%20a%20low%20price.%20So%20in%20a%20way%2C%20Indian%20investors%20earned%20even%20in%20this%20period.%20No%20one%20suffered%20a%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20retail%20investors%20benefited%20during%20the%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20demanded%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20(JPC)%20probe%2C%20terming%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20stock%20market%20scam.%26quot%3B%20Addressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said%20that%20after%20'fake'%20exit%20polls%2C%20stock%20markets%20rose%2C%20and%20then%20crashed%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20stocks%20witnessed%20a%20bloodbath%20on%20the%20day%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20were%20announced%20as%20the%20incumbent%20BJP%20performed%20below%20par%20and%20seemed%20it%20may%20fall%20short%20of%20exit%20poll%20predictions%20and%20the%20majority%20mark%20on%20its%20own.%20Many%20investors%20booked%20the%20profits%20they%20accumulated%20from%20the%20gains%20they%20made%20a%20day%20after%20the%20exit%20poll%20predictions%20indicated%20a%20comfortable%20majority%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensex%20declined%20by%20a%20whopping%204%2C389.73%20points%20and%20Nifty%20by%201%2C379.40%20points%20on%20the%20results%20day.%20Much%20of%20the%20losses%20have%20been%20recovered%20over%20the%20next%20two%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717732260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fjqo8q098_piyush-goyal_625x300_06_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-hits-back-at-congress-stock-market-charge-says-indian-investors-earned-on-june-4-5835879%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20on%20Thursday%20hit%20back%20at%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20who%20had%20alleged%20a%20connection%20between%20%26quot%3BBJP%2C%20exit%20pollsters%20and%20dubious%20foreign%20investors%26quot%3B.%20It%20also%20accused%20the%20Congress%20leader%20of%20%26quot%3Bconspiring%20to%20mislead%20market%20investors%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-hits-back-at-congress-stock-market-charge-says-indian-investors-earned-on-june-4-5835879%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-hits-back-at-congress-stock-market-charge-says-indian-investors-earned-on-june-4-5835879%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-hits-back-at-congress-stock-market-charge-says-indian-investors-earned-on-june-4-5835879%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Maharashtra%3A%20A%20Lesson%20For%20Assembly%20Polls%20Against%20'Jod-Tod'%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Fqr2q5ltg_sharad-pawar-uddhav-press-conference-pti-650_650x400_24_November_19.jpg%3Fim%3DResize%3D(1230%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Felections%2Fmaharashtra-state-lok-sabha-election-results-2024%5C%22%3ELok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20from%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20another%20political%20churn%20in%20the%20state%20before%20the%20assembly%20polls%20due%20in%20October%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Felections%2Fmaharashtra-state-lok-sabha-election-results-2024%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Congress%20would%20like%20to%20believe%20it%20was%20a%20test%20of%20Brand%20Modi's%20popularity%2C%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-day-lok-sabha-results-live-in-maharashtra-ogs-uddhav-thackeray-sharad-pawar-stand-tall-5814326%5C%22%3Efour%20regional%20parties%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20born%20out%20of%20splits%20in%20their%20mother%20organisations%2C%20it%20was%20always%20about%20settling%20legacy%20issues%20and%20asserting%20dominance%20before%20the%20real%20battle%20begins%20for%20the%20control%20of%20an%20industrialised%2C%20cash-rich%20state%20that%20is%20home%20to%20the%20country's%20financial%20capital%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20wealthiest%20civic%20body%2C%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Inevitable%20Verdict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20nearly%20four%20decades%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20-%20now%20split%20into%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Shinde)%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fuddhav-thackeray-is-not-joining-nda-sharad-pawar-s-ncp-800612%5C%22%3EUddhav%20Bal%20Thackeray%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20UBT)%2C%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%20and%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar)%20-%20have%20been%20the%20pivots%20on%20which%20Maharashtra%20politics%20turns.%20After%20two%20years%20of%20dramatic%20twists%20and%20turns%20in%20both%20parties%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20change%20of%20government%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20an%20ugly%20division%20in%20Maharashtra's%20political%20first%20family%20(the%20Pawars)%2C%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde%20from%20outside%20the%20bloodline%20laying%20claim%20to%20Bal%20Thackeray's%20bequest%2C%20it%20was%20inevitable%20that%20the%20soap%20operas%20playing%20out%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP%20would%20shape%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20results%20that%20the%20sympathy%20factor%20weighed%20heavily%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20voters%20as%20they%20gave%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20combo%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20the%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%20and%20the%20Congress%20the%20majority%20of%20the%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%20won%20eight%20of%20the%2010%20seats%20it%20contested%2C%20the%20Sena%20(UBT)%20bagged%20nine%20of%20the%2021%20it%20fought%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20stunned%20by%20emerging%20as%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20alliance%20with%2013%20seats%20out%20of%20the%2017%20assigned%20to%20it.%20That's%20a%20grand%20total%20of%2030%20of%20Maharashtra's%2048%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-not-joining-bjp-led-nda-working-to-install-maha-vikas-aghadi-govt-ncp-sp-leader-5832333%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Uddhav%20Thackeray%20Is%20Not%20Joining%20NDA%3A%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20only%20managed%2017%20seats.%20The%20party%20was%20the%20worst%20sufferer%20as%20its%20tally%20fell%20to%20just%20nine%20from%20the%2023%20it%20won%20in%202019.%20Shinde's%20Sena%20bagged%20seven%20seats%20out%20of%20the%2014%20it%20contested%2C%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20got%20just%20one%20seat%20from%20the%20five%20it%20fought%20in.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20the%20Shinde%20Sena's%20strike%20rate%20is%20more%20impressive%20than%20that%20of%20its%20rival%20UBT%20faction%2C%20it%20was%20the%20battle%20in%20the%20six%20seats%20of%20Mumbai%20that%20has%20settled%20the%20bitterly%20contested%20emotive%20legacy%20question%20of%20which%20is%20the%20real%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan't%20Ride%20On%20Sympathy%20Alone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20founded%20by%20Bal%20Thackeray%20and%20has%20been%20the%20fiefdom%20of%20the%20united%20party%20for%20over%20three%20decades.%20The%20results%20prove%20that%20Brand%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20not%20the%20usurper%2C%20reigns%20supreme%20on%20his%20father's%20home%20turf.%20The%20Sena%20(UBT)%20won%20three%20of%20the%20four%20seats%20it%20contested%20and%20helped%20its%20ally%20Congress%20win%20one.%20The%20BJP%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20just%20one%20seat%20-%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal's%20Mumbai%20North%20-%20while%20Shinde's%20Sena%20scraped%20through%20in%20the%20remaining%20seat%20by%20a%20meagre%2048%20votes%20that%20came%20through%20postal%20ballots%20right%20at%20the%20end%20in%20a%20nail-biting%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20parties%20regroup%20for%20the%20upcoming%20battle%20to%20control%20Maharashtra%2C%20several%20other%20factors%20will%20come%20into%20play.%20After%20all%2C%20sympathy%20cannot%20be%20a%20permanent%20mood%20among%20voters.%20The%20BJP%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20will%20have%20to%20introspect%20why%20it%20lost%20so%20badly%20in%20its%20strongholds%20of%20Vidarbha%20and%20Marathwada%2C%20that%20too%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20left%20virtually%20headless%20after%20an%20exodus%20of%20leaders%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20including%20former%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-pawar-says-he-takes-full-responsibility-for-ncps-poor-performance-5835724%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0On%20Wife's%20Baramati%20Defeat%20To%20Cousin%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Says%20This%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgrarian%20distress%20has%20been%20rampant%20in%20these%20areas%20for%20several%20years%20and%20the%20Modi%20government's%20flip-flops%20on%20agricultural%20policies%20deepened%20anger%20among%20farmers.%20It%20is%20also%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20lost%20much%20of%20its%20Dalit%20base%20in%20these%20regions%20following%20the%20Opposition-stoked%20controversy%20over%20plans%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution.%20Maharashtra%20is%20the%20home%20state%20of%20the%20writer%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20and%20with%20Dalits%20forming%2010.5%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population%2C%20any%20perceived%20attack%20on%20Ambedkar's%20masterpiece%20was%20bound%20to%20alienate%20them.%20The%20BJP%20has%20paid%20a%20heavy%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20was%20the%20running%20controversy%20over%20the%20Maratha%20demand%20for%20OBC%20status%20and%20accompanying%20reservation%20benefits.%20The%20delay%20in%20bringing%20a%2010%25%20quota%20for%20Marathas%20hurt%20the%20BJP%20and%20Shinde's%20Sena%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP.%20Being%20partners%20in%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20latter%20were%20seen%20as%20collaborators%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20deny%20reservation%20benefits%20to%20Marathas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20BJP%20tried%20to%20stoke%20communal%20sentiments%20with%20an%20aggressive%20campaign%20against%20'love%20jihad'%2C%20voters%20seemed%20as%20unmoved%20by%20this%20as%20they%20were%20by%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAjit%20Pawar's%20humiliation%20at%20the%20hustings%20has%20settled%20the%20vexed%20issue%20long%20rocking%20the%20family%20of%20who%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20political%20heir%20is.%20His%20daughter%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20can%20now%20firmly%20claim%20the%20mantle%20even%20as%20Ajit%20Pawar%20will%20have%20to%20contemplate%20his%20next%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Answer%20To%20The%20Legacy%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legacy%20issue%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20also%20been%20settled%20in%20favour%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%20Analysts%20in%20Maharashtra%20foresee%20a%20run%20on%20Shinde's%20party%20and%20predict%20that%20many%20of%20his%20MLAs%20could%20go%20back%20to%20join%20Uddhav's%20faction.%20With%20assembly%20elections%20merely%20months%20away%2C%20desperation%20must%20be%20rising.%20Apparently%2C%20some%20of%20those%20leaders%20have%20already%20sent%20feelers%20to%20the%20Sena%20(UBT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20that%20has%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20drawing%20board%20as%20it%20reviews%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%20strategy%20it%20crafted%20in%202022%20to%20snatch%20the%20government%20from%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20by%20breaking%20his%20party%20and%20later%20splitting%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP.%20Will%20it%20try%20to%20woo%20Uddhav%20back%20by%20dangling%20the%20carrot%20of%20restoring%20to%20him%20the%20coveted%20Shiv%20Sena%20election%20symbol%2C%20currently%20with%20the%20Shinde%20faction%2C%20and%20certain%20properties%20that%20are%20currently%20the%20subject%20of%20dispute%20between%20the%20two%20factions%3F%20Or%20will%20it%20heed%20the%20punishment%20meted%20out%20by%20voters%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ejod-tod%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20that%20has%20marred%20the%20Maharashtra%20landscape%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stakes%20are%20high%20for%20all%20parties%20concerned%20because%20after%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20several%20long-pending%20local%20elections%20will%20also%20have%20to%20be%20held%2C%20including%20the%20polls%20for%20the%20coveted%20municipalities%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Pune.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717731840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Fqr2q5ltg_sharad-pawar-uddhav-press-conference-pti-650_650x400_24_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaharashtra-a-lesson-for-assembly-polls-against-jod-tod-politics-5836125%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Will%20parties%20heed%20the%20punishment%20meted%20out%20by%20voters%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20%26quot%3Bjod-tod%26quot%3B%20that%20has%20marred%20the%20Maharashtra%20landscape%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaharashtra-a-lesson-for-assembly-polls-against-jod-tod-politics-5836125%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22D-Day%20anniversary%20haunted%20by%20dwindling%20number%20of%20veterans%20and%20shadowed%20by%20Europe's%20new%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717731734000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110782997%2Cimgsize-814962.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fd-day-anniversary-hau