20on%20Tesla's%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20%E2%80%94%20made%20up%20of%20pension%20fund%20managers%2C%20an%20asset%20management%20firm%2C%20and%20a%20bank%20%E2%80%94%20also%20includes%20Amalgamated%20Bank%2C%20AkademikerPension%2C%20Nordea%20Asset%20Management%2C%20New%20York%20City%20Comptroller%20Brad%20Lander%2C%20SHARE%2C%20Unison%2C%20and%20United%20Church%20Funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%2C%20Lander%20wrote%20that%20Musk's%20decision%20to%20divert%20Nvidia%20chips%20away%20from%20Tesla%20%26quot%3Bshould%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bred%20flag%20to%20investors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sudden%20move%20adds%20to%20the%20growing%20concerns%20about%20Musk's%20commitment%20to%20Tesla%20and%20highlights%20his%20glaring%20conflicts%20of%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20pressing%20need%20at%20Tesla%20for%20a%20genuinely%20independent%20board%20that%20will%20ensure%20Musk%20prioritizes%20company%20interests.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Illian%2C%20the%20director%20of%20responsible%20investing%20for%20United%20Church%20Funds%2C%20similarly%20criticized%20Musk's%20move%20to%20delay%20the%20shipment%20of%20Nvidia%20chips%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bfurther%20evidence%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20pay%20package%20%26quot%3Bnever%20achieved%20its%20purpose%20of%20maintaining%20the%20attention%20of%20Tesla's%20CEO.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20all%20about%20Elon%20building%20an%20empire%20for%20himself%20with%20investor%20money%20and%20we%20can't%20let%20this%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20immediately%20clear%20how%20much%20Tesla%20stock%20the%20eight%20shareholders%20own%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20of%20the%20eight%20shareholders%2C%20including%20Amalgamated%20Bank%2C%20Unison%2C%20Nordea%2C%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Retirement%20System%2C%20and%20United%20Church%20Funds%2C%20represent%20more%20than%204.9%20million%20shares%20of%20Tesla%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Thursday%2C%20those%20shares%20are%20worth%20more%20than%20%24878%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespersons%20for%20SHARE%2C%20Nordea%2C%20and%20Unison%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comment%20or%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20eight%20shareholders%2C%20the%20California%20Public%20Employees'%20Retirement%20System%20(CalPERS)%2C%20which%20owns%20about%209.5%20million%20shares%20of%20Tesla%20stock%2C%20signaled%20it%20would%20vote%20against%20Musk's%20pay%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20the%20compensation%20is%20commensurate%20with%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20CalPERS%20CEO%20Marcie%20Frost%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20CalPERS%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment%20when%20asked%20about%20Musk's%20decision%20to%20divert%20the%20shipment%20of%20Nvidia%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-shareholders-criticize-elon-musk-nvidia-chips-pay-package-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717729095000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666248701cd3b17790443887%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-shareholders-criticize-elon-musk-nvidia-chips-pay-package-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20shareholders%20said%20the%20Nvidia%20chip%20delivery%20delay%20is%20more%20proof%20that%20Elon%20Musk%20doesn't%20deserve%20his%20pay%20package.%20Shareholders%20vote%20on%20June%2013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A378%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-shareholders-criticize-elon-musk-nvidia-chips-pay-package-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Medical%20Aspirants%20Flag%20Marks%20Inflation%20In%20NEET%2C%20NTA%20Denies%20Irregularities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeveral%20aspirants%20of%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET%20have%20alleged%20inflation%20of%20marks%20which%20led%20to%20a%20record%2067%20candidates%20bagging%20the%20top%20rank%2C%20including%20six%20from%20the%20same%20exam%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20any%20irregularities%20and%20said%20the%20changes%20made%20in%20the%20NCERT%20textbooks%20and%20grace%20marks%20for%20losing%20time%20at%20the%20examination%20centres%20are%20some%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20students%20scoring%20higher%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20announced%20by%20NTA%20on%20Wednesday%20evening%20saw%2067%20students%20sharing%20rank%20one%2C%20including%20six%20from%20same%20examination%20centre%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20NEET%20exam%2C%20now%20the%20NEET%20result%20is%20also%20in%20controversy.%20After%20the%20NEET%20results%20were%20declared%2C%20questions%20are%20being%20raised%20on%20six%20students%20from%20the%20same%20centre%20getting%20720%20out%20of%20720%20marks.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20many%20other%20irregularities%20related%20to%20the%20NEET%20exam%20have%20also%20come%20to%20light%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20due%20to%20paper%20leak%20and%20now%20due%20to%20result%20error%2C%20the%20future%20of%20lakhs%20of%20youth%20of%20the%20country%20is%20getting%20ruined.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20this%20government%20cannot%20get%20any%20paper%20done%20without%20leaking%20it.%20Sir%20claims%20to%20stop%20wars%20in%20foreign%20countries%20but%20he%20is%20unable%20to%20even%20stop%20paper%20leaks%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailing%20the%20reason%20behind%20inflation%20of%20marks%2C%20the%20NTA%20said%20it%20received%20representations%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20loss%20of%20time%20during%20conduct%20of%20the%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20cases%20and%20representations%20were%20considered%20by%20NTA%20and%20the%20normalisation%20formula%2C%20which%20has%20been%20devised%20and%20adopted%20by%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20vide%20its%20Judgment%20dated%2013.06.2018%2C%20was%20implemented%20to%20address%20the%20loss%20of%20time%20faced%20by%20the%20candidates%20of%20NEET%20(UG)%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20loss%20of%20examination%20time%20was%20ascertained%20and%20such%20candidates%20were%20compensated%20with%20grace%20marks.%20So%2C%20there%20marks%20can%20be%20718%20or%20719%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20allegations%20of%20unclear%20implementation%20of%20grace%20marks%2C%20a%20senior%20NTA%20official%20told%20PTI%20that%20the%20question%20paper%20was%20prepared%20using%20a%20new%20NCERT%20textbook.%20However%2C%20some%20students%20had%20old%20NCERT%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20received%20a%20representation%20on%20this%20issue%20as%20well%20due%20to%20which%20NTA%20had%20to%20assign%20five%20marks%20to%20all%20students%20who%20had%20marked%20one%20of%20the%20two%20options.%20Because%20of%20this%20reason%2C%20marks%20of%20a%20total%20of%2044%20students%20increased%20from%20715%20to%20720%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20an%20increased%20number%20of%20toppers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20court%20cases%20and%20representations%20raising%20concerns%20over%20loss%20of%20time%20during%20exam%20were%20received%2C%20a%20committee%20was%20formed%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20official%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20committee%20went%20through%20everything%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20time%20was%20ascertained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20candidates%20were%20compensated%20with%20grace%20marks.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20marks%20of%20students%20at%20some%20centres%20are%20high%20because%20it%20is%20likely%20they%20all%20benefitted%20from%20grace%20marks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%2C%20the%20mark%20inflation%20in%20NEET%20UG%202024%20result%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20securing%20a%20spot%20in%20medical%20school%20this%20year%20more%20difficult.%20Some%20aspiring%20students%20have%20turned%20to%20online%20platforms%20to%20demand%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20results%20and%20a%20re-examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20students%20are%20raising%20some%20valid%20points.%20How%20come%20students%20with%20same%20sequence%20roll%20number%20scored%20the%20same%20marks.%20This%20is%20a%20serious%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20such%20doctors%20to%20serve%20our%20country.%20This%20must%20be%20investigated%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anubha%20Shrivastava%2C%20a%20lawyer%20and%20president%20of%20India%20Wide%20Parents%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20aspirant%20took%20to%20X%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B67%20students%20scoring%20720%20out%20of%20720%20marks%20in%20the%20results%20released%20after%20the%20NEET%20exam%20paper%20leak%20raises%20suspicion.%20This%20is%20playing%20with%20the%20future%20of%20lakhs%20of%20candidates%20of%20the%20country%2C%20due%20to%20which%20there%20is%20anger%20among%20the%20students.%20The%20government%20should%20conduct%20a%20high-level%20investigation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20X%20user%20Nitish%20Rajput%20said%20NTA%20awarded%20grace%20marks%20according%20to%20the%20court%20order%20but%20the%20students%20argue%20this%20sudden%20decision%20is%20unjust%20as%20the%20agency%20has%20not%20mentioned%20any%20methodology%20to%20award%20these%20'grace%20marks'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCalls%20for%20transparency%20in%20the%20process%20have%20only%20grown%20louder.%20The%20controversy%20for%20the%20NTA%20is%20brewing%20as%20lakhs%20of%20students%20demand%20re-examination%20citing%20lack%20of%20clarity%20in%20NTA's%20explanations%20and%20have%20even%20pushed%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20intervention.%20Grace%20marks%20given%20for%20lost%20exam%20time%20have%20raised%20concerns%20of%20fairness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrance%20exam%20was%20conducted%20on%20May%205%20at%204%2C750%20centres%20in%20571%20cities%20including%2014%20cities%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NTA%20had%20on%20May%205%20claimed%20that%20the%20distribution%20of%20wrong%20question%20papers%20at%20an%20exam%20centre%20in%20Rajasthan%20led%20to%20some%20candidates%20walking%20out%20with%20the%20papers.%20The%20agency%20had%20denied%20any%20leak%20of%20the%20question%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20the%20NTA%20had%20reiterated%20that%20the%20reports%20claiming%20question%20paper%20leak%20in%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET-UG%20are%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20baseless%20and%20without%20any%20ground%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20every%20question%20paper%20has%20been%20accounted%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717729020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fprgp4jto_neet-ug-_625x300_28_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fmedical-aspirants-flag-marks-inflation-in-neet-nta-denies-irregularities-5832541%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20results%20announced%20by%20NTA%20saw%2067%20students%20sharing%20rank%20one%2C%20including%20six%20from%20same%20examination%20centre%20in%20Haryana.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fmedical-aspirants-flag-marks-inflation-in-neet-nta-denies-irregularities-5832541%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww