efeat%20To%20Cousin%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Says%20This%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20on%20Thursday%20took%20full%20responsibility%20for%20the%20NCP's%20poor%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20asserted%20the%20defeat%20in%20Baramati%2C%20viewed%20as%20a%20prestige%20battle%2C%20was%20surprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20after%20the%20meeting%20of%20his%20party%20MLAs%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%20all%20legislators%20were%20firmly%20with%20him%20and%20rejected%20speculation%20that%20some%20were%20planning%20to%20defect%20to%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20opposition%20can%20say%20anything.%20I%20have%20always%20had%20the%20support%20of%20the%20people.%20My%20MLAs%2C%20MLCs%20have%20assured%20me%20they%20will%20always%20stand%20by%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Baramati%2C%20where%20sitting%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20defeated%20his%20wife%20Sunetra%20Pawar%20by%20a%20huge%20margin%2C%20the%20deputy%20CM%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20result%20is%20surprising%20since%20I%20always%20had%20the%20support%20of%20the%20people%20there.%26quot%3B%20Queried%20about%20whether%20he%20would%20once%20again%20join%20hands%20with%20NCP%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20he%20tersely%20said%20he%20accepted%20responsibility%20for%20the%20poll%20debacle%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20need%20to%20bring%20family%20matters%20in%20public%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20there%20would%20be%20detailed%20introspection%20of%20the%20party's%20poll%20performance%2C%20the%20NCP%20president%20said%20some%20of%20the%20reasons%20included%20Muslims%20moving%20away%20from%20the%20ruling%20alliance%2C%20the%20Opposition's%20allegations%20of%20change%20in%20Constitution%2C%20which%20alienated%20the%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20classes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20ongoing%20Maratha%20quota%20stir%20in%20Marathwada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20said%20he%20had%20discussed%20the%20results%20with%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20asserted%20appropriate%20decisions%20would%20be%20taken%20to%20win%20back%20the%20support%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20said%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20Deputy%20CM%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20over%20the%20latter's%20statement%20about%20quitting%20his%20post%20following%20the%20poll%20debacle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFadnavis%20said%20we%20shall%20talk%20about%20it%20in%20Delhi%20tomorrow.%20I%20am%20going%20to%20Delhi%20tomorrow%20for%20the%20NDA%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20party%20MLC%20Amol%20Mitkari%20commenting%20on%20internal%20sabotage%20and%20lack%20of%20support%20of%20allies%20having%20caused%20the%20loss%20in%20Baramati%20and%20Shirur%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%20his%20colleague%20had%20got%20the%20%26quot%3Bwrong%20briefing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20fell%20short%20and%20I%20take%20full%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQueried%20on%20whether%20the%20poll%20loss%20was%20a%20message%20from%20people%20that%20they%20did%20not%20approve%20of%20defections%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20won%20seven%20out%20of%2015%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefections%20are%20not%20new%20to%20Maharashtra.%20It%20happened%20in%201978%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20reference%20to%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20move%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20veteran%20becoming%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20split%20in%20July%20last%20year%20after%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20eight%20MLAs%20joined%20the%20Shinde%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publi