e%20away%20just%2013%20runs%20for%20a%20famous%20win.%20As%20Netravalkar%20steered%20USA%20to%20victory%2C%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20as%20fans%20lauded%20the%20'software%20engineer'%20from%20Oracle%20who%20made%20history%20at%20the%20biggest%20stage%20in%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20LinkedIn%20headline%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BPrincipal%20Member%20of%20Technical%20Staff%20at%20Oracle%2C%20Professional%20Cricketer%26quot%3B.%20It's%20time%20to%20swap%20these%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20LinkedIn%20Profile%20of%20SAURABH%20NETRAVALKAR%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqBn5HajI30%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqBn5HajI30%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Johns.%20(%40CricCrazyJohns)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCricCrazyJohns%2Fstatus%2F1798809242792776107%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20humbling%20feeling%20that%20life%20has%20given%20me%20a%20second%20chance%20to%20pursue%20what%20I%20love%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Netravalkar%20said%20after%20the%20match.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20really%20feel%20that%20bliss%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20walk%20onto%20the%20field%20to%20play%20competitive%20cricket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20match%2C%20USA%20thus%20jumped%20to%20the%20top%20of%20Group%20A%20with%20two%20wins%20from%20as%20many%20games%20ahead%20of%20the%20clash%20against%20India.%20USA%20had%20defeated%20Canada%20by%20seven%20wickets%20in%20their%20opener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpting%20to%20field%2C%20left-arm%20spinner%20Nosthush%20Kenjige%20scalped%20three%20wickets%20for%2030%20runs%20as%20Pakistan%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20press%20the%20accelerator%20and%20were%20restricted%20to%20159%20for%20seven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20chasing%2C%20USA%20ended%20on%20the%20same%20score%2C%20reaching%20159%20for%203%20with%20skipper%20Monank%20Patel%20(50%20off%2038)%2C%20Aaron%20Jones%20(36%20not%20out%20of%2026)%20and%20Andries%20Gous%20(35%20off%2026)%20leading%20from%20the%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20embarrassment%20for%20Pakistan%2C%20they%20took%20longer%20time%20than%20usual%20to%20come%20out%20to%20bat%20in%20the%20Super%20Over%2C%20keeping%20the%20USA%20fielders%20waiting%20and%20getting%20the%20on-field%20umpires%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20USA's%20decision%20to%20bowl%20first%20worked%20as%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20was%20dismissed%20in%20the%20second%20over%2C%20caught%20by%20Steven%20Taylor%20off%20Netravalkar%20(2%2F18).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSA%20started%20their%20chase%20on%20a%20bright%20note%2C%20scoring%2044%20runs%20in%20the%20powerplay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20led%20from%20the%20front%20as%20he%20played%20his%20shots%20to%20pick%20up%20consecutive%20boundaries%20off%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20in%20the%20fourth%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseem%20Shah%20gave%20Pakistan%20the%20first%20breakthrough%20when%20Taylor%20nicked%20one%20to%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20behind%20the%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBur%20new%20man%20Andries%20Gous%20meant%20business%20as%20he%20picked%20up%20two%20fours%20in%20the%20same%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGous%20was%20particularly%20elegant%20square%20of%20the%20wicket%20as%20he%20just%20opened%20his%20bat%20a%20bit%20to%20pick%20up%20another%20four%20off%20Haris%20Rauf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUSA's%20body%20language%20was%20positive%20with%20Patel%20and%20Gous%20leading%20the%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20showed%20his%20prowess%20through%20the%20off-side%2C%20picking%20up%20two%20consecutive%20boundaries%20off%20Iftikhar%20Ahmed%20through%20the%20cover%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20was%20at%20his%20destructive%20best%20as%20he%20first%20hit%20Afridi%20over%20mid-off%20for%20a%20boundary%20and%20then%20clobbered%20the%20bowler%20over%20his%20head%20for%20a%2