0Haris%20Rauf%20bowled%20the%20final%20delivery%20to%20USA's%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20the%20traffic%20signal%20at%20the%20WTC%20reportedly%20paused%20for%20a%20few%20seconds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Fwhen-traffic-signal-at-new-yorks-wtc-dropped-out-for-the-final-ball-of-pakistan-vs-usa-match-in-t20-world-cup%2Farticleshow%2F110780924.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20officers%20to%20join%20search%20for%20Michael%20Mosley%20as%20his%20disappearance%20is%20described%20as%20'strange'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717725600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F06%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-dr-michael-mosley-daily-mail-columnist_6574701.jpg%3F20240606124007%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmichael-mosley-more-officers-to-join-search-for-tv-doctor-on-greek-island-as-his-disappearance-is-described-as-strange-13149151%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20search%20for%20missing%20TV%20doctor%20Michael%20Mosley%20will%20continue%20on%20Friday%20with%20more%20officers%2C%20according%20to%20police%20on%20the%20Greek%20island%20of%20Symi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmichael-mosley-more-officers-to-join-search-for-tv-doctor-on-greek-island-as-his-disappearance-is-described-as-strange-13149151%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmichael-mosley-more-officers-to-join-search-for-tv-doctor-on-greek-island-as-his-disappearance-is-described-as-strange-13149151%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmichael-mosley-more-officers-to-join-search-for-tv-doctor-on-greek-island-as-his-disappearance-is-described-as-strange-13149151%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ICC%20Breaks%20Silence%20Over%20Criticism%20Surrounding%20IND%20vs%20IRE%20Pitch%20In%20T20%20WC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Nassau%20County%20ground's%20track%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bbordering%20on%20dangerous%20with%20huge%20open%20cracks%26quot%3B%2C%20has%20become%20a%20concern%20in%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20ICC%20on%20Thursday%20conceded%20that%20the%20tracks%20used%20so%20far%20%26quot%3Bhave%20not%20played%20as%20consistently%20as%20we%20would%20have%20all%20wanted%26quot%3B.%20The%20concerns%20were%20heightened%20after%20India%20opened%20their%20campaign%20with%20an%20eight-wicket%20win%20in%20a%20low-scoring%20match%20against%20Ireland%2C%20who%20were%20bowled%20out%20of%2096%20in%20just%2016%20overs.%20India%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20who%20scored%20a%20half%20century%20in%20the%20successful%20chase%2C%20was%20hit%20on%20his%20right%20bicep%20by%20pacer%20Josh%20Little%20and%20was%20forced%20to%20retire%20hurt.%20The%20ball%20that%20struck%20him%20suddenly%20took%20off%20from%20length%20on%20a%20pitch%20that%20offered%20a%20great%20degree%20of%20uneven%20bounce.%20Rishabh%20Pant%20was%20also%20hit%20on%20his%20left%20elbow%20during%20his%2036%20not%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInjury%20scare%20aside%2C%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20pitch%2C%20a%20drop-in%20one%20brought%20from%20Adelaide%20specifically%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20has%20raised%20eyebrows.%20India%20are%20scheduled%20to%20play%20two%20more%20games%20at%20this%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20former%20players%20like%20Irfan%20Pathan%2C%20Michael%20Vaughan%20and%20Sanjay%20Manjrekar%20called%20the%20track%20unsuitable%20for%20T20s%20especially%20when%20the%20event%20is%20being%20promoted%20as%20cricket's%20entry%20into%20the%20unexplored%20American%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BT20%20Inc%20and%20the%20ICC%20recognise%20that%20the%20pitches%20used%20so%20far%20at%20the%20Nassau%20County%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20have%20not%20played%20as%20consistently%20as%20we%20would%20have%20all%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ICC%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world-class%20grounds%20team%20have%20been%20working%20hard%20since%20the%20conclusion%20of%20yesterday's%20game%20to%20remedy%20the%20situation%20and%20deliver%20the%20best%20possible%20surfaces%20for%20the%20remaining%20matches%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20fit%20for%20the%20marquee%20clash%20against%20Pakistan%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohit's%20injury%20isn't%20serious.%20He%20himself%20said%20that%20it's%20a%20bit%20sore.%20He%20should%20be%20okay%20for%20Pakistan%20game%20(on%20Sunday)%20as%20of%20now.%20There%20are%20two%20practice%20sessions%20before%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20BCCI%20source%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayer%20of%20the%20final%20from%20India's%202007%20T20%20World%20Cup%20triumph%2C%20Pathan%2C%20hardly%20minced%20words%20as%20he%20criticised%20the%20pitch%2C%20calling%20it%20unsafe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20we%20definitely%20want%20to%20promote%20cricket%20in%20America%2C%20but%20this%20pitch%20is%20not%20safe%20for%20players.%20If%20we%20had%20a%20pitch%20like%20this%20in%20India%2C%20a%20match%20would%20never%20be%20played%20there%20again%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20pitch%20is%20definitely%20not%20good.%20I%20mean%2C%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20the%20World%20Cup%20here%2C%20not%20even%20a%20bilateral%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20unimpressed%20was%20former%20England%20captain%20Vaughan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrying%20to%20sell%20the%20game%20in%20the%20states%20is%20great..%20love%20it..%20but%20for%20players%20to%20have%20to%20play%20on%20this%20sub-standard%20surface%20in%20New%20York%20is%20unacceptable%E2%80%A6%20You%20work%20so%20hard%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20WC%20then%20have%20to%20play%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20his%20X%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20was%20bewildered%20by%20the%20track's%20behaviour%20and%20conceded%20that%20he%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20expect%20from%20it%20against%20Pakistan.%20The%20team's%20batting%20coach%20Vikram%20Rathour%20was%20a%20shade%20more%20reticent%20in%20his%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20challenging%20wicket%20as%20far%20as%20batting%20is%20concerned%20but%20this%20is%20what%20we%20have.%20So%20we%20need%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20deal%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Rathour%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%2C%20placing%20the%20onus%20on%20his%20team%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20management%20is%20unlikely%20to%20file%20any%20official%20complaint.%20But%20the%20displeasure%20is%20clear%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20track%2C%20which%20according%20to%20some%20who%20saw%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bunfit%20for%20T20%20cricket%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbordering%20on%20dangerous%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20actually%20a%20very%20fresh%20pitch.%20There%20is%20a%20grass%20cover%20but%20along%20with%20it%20are%20big%20cracks.%20So%2C%20it%20will%20seam%20but%20also%20take%20off%20from%20length.%20Now%20when%20you%20have%20a%20fresh%20track%20like%20this%2C%20you%20first%20try%20out%20a%20few%20games%20like%20you%20do%20with%20beta%20testing%20of%20a%20new%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20you%20release%20it%20in%20the%20market.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20T20%20wicket%20and%20all%20four%20tracks%20look%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20source%20after%20a%20first-hand%20look%20at%20the%20track%20following%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMay%20be%20a%20roller%20would%20even%20out%20the%20cracks%20but%20such%20pitches%20are%20known%20to%20take%20time%20to%20settle%20for%20batting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Indian%20pacers%20literally%20toyed%20with%20a%20very%20competent%20T20%20outfit%20like%20Ireland%2C%20even%20the%20biggest%20fan%20of%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20wouldn't%20have%20imagined%20that%20his%20deliveries%20would%20take%20off%20like%20surface%20to%20air%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20should%20be%20glad%20that%20nothing%20serious%20happened%20to%20Rohit%20and%20Rishabh%20(Pant).%20They%20are%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ireland's%20Harry%20Tector%20had%20to%20undergo%20a%20mandatory%20concussion%20test%20after%20a%20nasty%20snorter%20from%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20first%20hit%20his%20gloves%20and%20then%20flush%20on%20the%20helmet%20before%20Virat%20Kohli%20completed%20the%20catch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20rules%20on%20quality%20of%20pitches%20are%20quite%20clear.%20An%20assessment%20would%20only%20be%20done%20once%20the%20tournament%20is%20over%20and%20if%20found%20sub-standard%2C%20the%20track's%20overall%20rating%20would%20go%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20chorus%20of%20criticism%20was%20former%20Zimbabwe%20captain%20and%20renowed%20coach%20Andy%20Flower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20got%20to%20say%20that%20is%20not%20a%20good%20surface%20to%20play%20an%20international%20match%20on.%20It's%20bordering%20on%20dangerous%2C%26quot%3B%20Flower%20said%20on%20'ESPNcricinfo's%20Timeout'%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20batter%20Sanjay%20Manjrekar%20feels%20the%20pitch%20is%20under-prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20seen%20dangerous%20pitches%20before%20as%20well%20at%20the%20international%20level%20but%20something%20has%20gone%20wrong%20with%20the%20preparation%20where%20either%20the%20pitch%20has%20been%20under-prepared%20or%20something%20that%20is%20beyond%20their%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Manjrekar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717725420000%2C%22