0job.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%2036%20guests%2C%20we%20upgraded%20to%20their%20larger%20chapel%20and%20got%20the%20basic%20photo%20package%20as%20backup%20in%20case%20the%20photographer%20we%20hired%20last%20minute%20had%20an%20issue.%20Luckily%2C%20there%20was%20no%20issue%20with%20the%20photographer%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.keithkaplanphotographylasvegas.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKeith%20Kaplan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20was%20fantastic.%20I'm%20glad%20I%20listened%20to%20my%20gut%20on%20getting%20the%20backup%20%E2%80%94%20it%20turns%20out%20you%20can't%20have%20too%20many%20pictures%20of%20your%20wedding.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20the%20best%20moment%20of%20the%20day%20was%20seeing%20our%20family%20and%20close%20friends%20gathered%20outside%20The%20Little%20White%20Chapel%2C%20waiting%20for%20us%20when%20we%20pulled%20up.%20Our%20photographer%20was%20driving%2C%20and%20I%20was%20too%20busy%20taking%20it%20in%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20picture%20of%20that%20moment%2C%20but%20it%20is%20etched%20in%20my%20brain.%20It%20was%20so%20touching%20to%20see%20who%20came%20to%20support%20us%20and%20feel%20their%20love.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de7001b8-cece-410b-81b7-8a023dc77261%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20accommodations%20for%20every%20budget%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20upside%20of%20a%20destination%20wedding%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flas-vegas-things-you-should-never-do-during-first-visit-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELas%20Vegas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20that%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20cheap%20flights%20and%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20accommodations%20in%20different%20price%20ranges%2C%20so%20we%20didn't%20feel%20like%20it%20was%20overly%20burdensome%20for%20our%20guests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E