ner%252Cof%252520the%252520bill%252520%252852%252525%2529.%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Knot%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20it's%20more%20common%20for%20couples%20and%20their%20families%20to%20split%20the%20costs%20equally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20their%20daughter%2C%20and%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20were%20all%20happy%20with%20the%20lump-sum%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20they%20kind%20of%20tricked%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20laughing.%20%26quot%3BOne%20day%2C%20they%20came%20home%20and%20said%2C%20'Hey%2C%20we%20bought%20a%20house.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20took%20the%20%2420%2C000%20and%20used%20it%20to%20put%20a%20down%20payment%20on%20their%20home%20%E2%80%94%20before%20they%20actually%20had%20their%20wedding%2C%20which%20they%20then%20planned%20to%20pay%20for%20out%20of%20their%20own%20pocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Mike%20was%20surprised%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20he%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20good%20thing%20that%20his%20daughter%20and%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20paid%20for%20their%20own%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20kids%20are%20not%20given%20carte%20blanche%20on%20wedding%20plans%2C%20if%20they're%20forced%20to%20budget%20from%20their%20own%20standpoint%2C%20the%20whole%20thing%20just%20doesn't%20get%20out%20of%20hand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20held%20the%20wedding%20at%20the%20rose%20garden%20in%20Loose%20Park%2C%20a%20large%20public%20park%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-cost-of-living-nyc-kansas-city-midwest-rent-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKansas%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20at%20a%20popular%20reception%20hall.%20Mike%20said%20everything%20about%20the%20wedding%20seemed%20reasonable%20but%20that%20he%20never%20learned%20what%20they%20ended%20up%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20asked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20coup