ne%20venture%20is%20quietly%20arming%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fsarahemerson%2F2024%2F06%2F06%2Feric-schmidt-is-secretly-testing-ai-military-drones-in-a-wealthy-silicon-valley-suburb%2F%3Fsh%3D6f242b807d6f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20ex-Google%20CEO's%20secretive%20company%20has%20poached%20roughly%20a%20dozen%20employees%20from%20Apple%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20more%20over%20the%20past%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20aims%20to%20develop%20drones%20that%20harness%20AI%20to%20accurately%20strike%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20sourced%20key%20candidates%20from%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20Schmidt's%20own%20nonprofit%20organization%2C%20Schmidt%20Futures%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Schmidt%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20has%20been%20building%20the%20venture%20quietly.%20First%20revealed%20to%20be%20named%20White%20Stork%20by%20Forbes%2C%20the%20outlet%20reports%20it's%20since%20been%20renamed%20Project%20Eagle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForbes%20reports%20the%20company%20has%20been%20testing%20AI-guided%20drones%20both%20from%20Hillspire%20%E2%80%94%20Schmidt's%20family%20office%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20where%20he's%20visited%20on%20multiple%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-eric-schmidt-ai-attack-drones-white-stork-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeen%20outspoken%20about%20his%20belief%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20AI%20could%20revolutionize%20modern%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fopinion%2Finternational%2F4602883-ukraine-needs-one-more-year-to-win-and-congress-can-make-that-happen-now%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20penned%20an%20op-ed%3C%2Fa%3E%20encouraging%20Congress%20to%20approve%20an%20aid%20package%20that%20would%20give%20%2460%20billion%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilitary%20affairs%20and%20AI%20are%20long-held%20passions%20for%20the%20tech%20luminary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20departing%20Google%2C%20Schmidt%20served%20as%20chair%20of%20both%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense's%20Innovation%20Board%20and%20the%20National%20Security%20Commission%20on%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e2c9838-ed0e-444e-9c66-5f4b36936771%5C%22%3EAI%20comes%20to%20the%20battlefield%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20may%20once%20have%20seemed%20like%20science%20fiction%2C%20AI%20is%20already%20making%20an%20impact%20in%20modern%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-using-ai-gaza-targets-terrifying-glimpse-at-future-war-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eused%20AI%20to%20identify%20targets%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fire%20on%20during%20its%20ongoing%20war%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20think%20AI%20could%20revolutionize%20decision-making%20in%20war%20time%2C%20and%20reduce%20costs%20as%20military%20leaders%20simulate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-could-shape-future-of-war-starting-with-wargaming-experts-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewar%20games%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20strategize%20what%20could%20happen%20in%20future%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20others%20have%20warned%20against%20the%20rapid%20adoption%20of%20AI%20in%20combat%2C%20questioning%20whether%20legal%20and%20ethical%20considerations%20are%20moving%20fast%20enough%20in%20step%20to%20keep%20it%20in%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-schmidt-poaches-apple-spacex-google-ai-drones-report-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717706154000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.c