%20but%20not%20on%20Thursday%2C%20though%20the%20game%20ended%20in%20a%20draw%20this%20time%20also.%20He%20also%20did%20not%20have%20much%20to%20show%20for%20in%20the%20whole%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20151st%20match%20for%20the%20country%2C%20Chhetri%20gave%20a%20last%20bow%2C%20taking%20a%20lap%20of%20honour%20of%20the%20packed%20venue%20with%20folded%20hands%20as%20chants%20of%20%26quot%3BSunil%2C%20Sunil%26quot%3B%20echoed%20the%20stands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuwait%20looked%20a%20much%20improved%20side%20from%20the%20last%20time%20when%20they%20suffered%20a%200-1%20defeat%20to%20India%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first-half%20saw%20a%20flurry%20of%20activities%2C%20with%20both%20teams%20creating%20chances%20but%20failing%20to%20find%20the%20back%20of%20the%20net.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20action%20on%20the%20field%20kept%20the%20fans%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20their%20seats%20as%20they%20kept%20screaming%20%26quot%3BSunil%2C%20Sunil%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BVande%20Mataram%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuwait's%20best%20chance%20of%20the%20first-half%20came%20in%20the%20fourth%20minute%20when%20Eid%20Al-Rashidi%20threaded%20a%20perfect%20through%20ball%20to%20Daham%2C%20who%20surged%20past%20Nikhil%20Poojary.%20Mohammad%20Daham's%20effort%20was%20denied%20by%20a%20crucial%20save%20from%20the%20Indian%20goalkeeper%20Gurpreet%20Singh%20Sandhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2011th%20minute%2C%20India%20responded%20as%20Liston%20Colaco%20surged%20from%20the%20left%20wing%2C%20sending%20in%20a%20low%20cross%20as%20all%20eyes%20focused%20on%20Chhetri's%2095th%20goal.%20But%20Hasan%20Alanezi's%20sliding%20clearance%20thwarted%20the%20Indian%20captain's%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20ensuing%20corner%2C%20Anwar%20Ali's%20header%20just%20missed%20the%20target%2C%20much%20to%20the%20crowd's%20anticipation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Rashidi%20latched%20onto%20a%20chipped%20pass%20from%20Al-Harbi%2C%20but%20his%20attempted%20chip%20over%20Gurpreet%20sailed%20over%20the%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2025th%20minute%2C%20the%20debutant%20Jay%20Gupta%20was%20in%20thick%20of%20action.%20Gupta%20delivered%20a%20sublime%20low%20cross%20from%20the%20left%2C%20but%20the%20Kuwait%20defense%20cleared%20it%20for%20a%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20failed%20to%20utilise%20a%20freekick%20in%20the%2028th%20minute%20when%20Poojary%20showcased%20his%20skills%20with%20a%20superb%20run%20down%20the%20right%20wing%2C%20nutmegging%20a%20defender%20before%20being%20brought%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThapa's%20delivery%2C%20however%2C%20didn't%20yield%20a%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20at%20the%20halfway%20mark%2C%20Thapa%20sent%20a%20fantastic%20ball%20into%20the%20box%2C%20which%20Kuwait%20could%20only%20clear%20to%20deny%20Sahal%20Abdul%20Samad.%20His%20left-footed%20shot%20was%20blocked%2C%20and%20the%20rebound%20fell%20to%20Liston%20Colaco%2C%20who%20fired%20a%20low%20strike%20into%20the%20side%20netting%20from%20a%20narrow%20angle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuwait%2C%20frustrated%20by%20Gupta's%20defensive%20efforts%2C%20switched%20play%20from%20the%20right%20to%20the%20left%2C%20only%20for%20the%20move%20to%20end%20with%20the%20ball%20going%20out%20of%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIgor%20Stimac%20made%20a%20bold%20move%20by%20shuffling%20their%20attacking%20lineup%2C%20introducing%20Rahim%20Ali%20up%20front%20with%20Brandon%20Fernandes%20and%20Chheri%20behind%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20failed%20to%20yield%20the%20desired%20result%20as%20he%20failed%20to%20convert%20his%20chances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2047th%20minute%2C%20Faisal%20Al-Harbi%20tested%20Gurpreet%20with%20a%20low%20volley%2C%20but%20India's%20custodian%20stood%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20minute%20later%2C%20Rahim%20found%20himself%20one-on-one%20with%20the%20Kuwait%20keeper%20Sulaiman%20Abdulghafor%2C%20but%20couldn't%20convert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20India's%20openness%20at%20the%20back%2C%20Gurpreet's%20brilliance%20denied%20Kuwait's%20Rashidi%20just%20moments%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20asserted%20dominance%2C%20Kuwait's%20frustration%20peaked%20in%20the%2074th%20minute%20with%20a%20denied%20penalty%20claim%2C%20incensing%20players%20and%20bench%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplays%20suggested%20a%20foul%2C%20but%20the%20Chinese%20referee%20Fu%20Ming%20deemed%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETempers%20flared%20up%20to%20a%20mini-brawl%20after%20a%20challenge%20on%20Indian%20debutant%20Edmund%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20confrontation%20between%20him%20and%20Sultan%20Alenezi%2C%20both%20receiving%20yellow%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20tension%2C%20Edmund%20rallied%20the%20crowd's%20support%20with%20a%20free-kick%20opportunity%2C%20but%20Brandon%20Fernandes'%20atrocious%20delivery%20meant%20India's%20last%20hope%20for%20a%20win%20went%20up%20in%20smoke%20in%20the%20added%20seven%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStimac%20handed%20left-back%20Gupta%20international%20debut%20in%20his%204-2-3-1%20formation%20with%20Chhetri%20the%20sole%20striker%20up%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20months%20back%20Gupta%20made%20his%20league%20debut%20for%20FC%20Goa%20in%20the%20top%20tier%20Indian%20Super%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717692120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm5pq2is_s_625x300_06_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fsunil-chhetri-in-tears-gets-guard-of-honour-after-farewell-match-watch-5833711%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Chhetri%20stirred%20up%20emotions%20in%20his%20final%20international%20outing%20but%20the%20Indian%20football%20team%20just%20could%20not%20rise%20to%20the%20occasion%20as%20it%20settled%20for%20a%20goal-less%20draw%20against%20Kuwait.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fsunil-chhetri-in-tears-gets-guard-of-honour-after-farewell-match-watch-5833711%22%