ardware%2C%20networking%20and%20programming.%20He%20learnt%20from%20tutorials%20on%20Google%20and%20YouTube%2C%20following%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20late%20Kevin%20Mitnick%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20hackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20that%20we%20can%20secure%20data%20for%20organisations.%20Even%20though%20companies%20have%20their%20own%20security%20teams%2C%20they%20invite%20ethical%20hackers%20to%20report%20vulnerabilities%20in%20their%20data%20through%20their%20responsible%20disclosure%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20343%20million%20people%20have%20been%20the%20victims%20of%20cyber%20attacks%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Forbes%20report.%20Data%20breaches%20also%20saw%20a%2072%20percent%20increase%20in%202023%20compared%20to%202021%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20need%20for%20ethical%20hackers%20and%20cyber%20security%20experts%20all%20the%20more%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Class%2012%2C%20Muneeb%20pursued%20a%20B.Tech%20in%20Computer%20Science%20in%20a%20college%20which%20was%2080%20km%20away.%20The%20daily%20travel%20and%20classes%20left%20him%20with%20no%20time%20to%20pursue%20his%20passion.%20Supported%20by%20his%20father%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20drop%20out%20in%20the%20second%20year%20to%20focus%20entirely%20on%20ethical%20hacking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20either%20complete%20my%20engineering%20degree%20or%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F231525%2Fcyfirma-startup-cybersecurity-chinese-hackers-india-cert-malware-phishing-dark-web-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20follow%20my%20passion%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20a%20BCA%20degree%20in%20cyber%20security%20which%20also%20allowed%20me%20the%20time%20to%20hone%20my%20skills%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2022-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20now%20pursuing%20BCA%20through%20correspondence%20from%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20National%20Open%20University%20(IGNOU).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Muneeb%20Amin%20Bhat%20with%20his%20setup%20at%20home%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352032%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMuneeb%20Amin%20Bhat%20with%20his%20setup%20at%20home%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20Apple%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20user%20data%20leak%20on%20iCloud.%20I%20submitted%20my%20findings%20in%20July%202023%20and%20received%20an%20acknowledgement%20from%20them%20a%20few%20months%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20developed%20his%20own%20interception%20tools%20that%20help%20him%20test%20data%20and%20find%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20family%20was%20initially%20hesitant%20about%20his%20choice%2C%20the%20growth%20of%20cybersecurity%20as%20a%20viable%20career%20option%20and%20the%20financial%20rewards%20doled%20out%20by%20companies%20for%20identifying%20breaches%20in%20their%20data%20helped%20convince%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalled%20%E2%80%98bug%20bounties%E2%80%99%2C%20companies%20offer%20anywhere%20from%20%24100%20to%20%2410%2C000%20per%20vulnerability.%20The%20reward%20increases%20depending%20on%20the%20criticality%20of%20the%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuneeb%20wishes%20to%20join%20a%20company%20as%20a%20cybersecurity%20analyst%20after%20completing%20his%20degree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20user%20data%20and%20company%20websites%20and%20domains%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340888%2Fshark-tank-cybersecurity-app-artificial-intelligence-ai-pratyusha-vemuri-online-fraud-transactions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ethical%20hacking%20space%20is%20a%20growing%20one%20with%20multiple%20jobs%20opening%20up%20for%20the%20same%20in%20India%20and%20abroad.%20For%20anyone%20interested%20in%20getting%20into%20this%20space%2C%20more%20than%20degrees%2C%20Muneeb%20states%20that%20self-learning%20and%20knowledge%20about%20the%20hardware%2C%20operating%20systems%2C%20and%20networking%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20basic%20computer%20degree%20like%20a%20BCA%20or%20MCA%20or%20BTech%20would%20be%20good%20to%20enter%20into%20this%20field.%20Certifications%20like%20OSCP%20(Offensive%20Security%20Certified%20Professional)%20and%20CEH%20(Certified%20Ethical%20Hacker)%20will%20add%20value%20to%20your%20resume.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%20important%20is%20to%20learn%20about%20computer%20hardware%2C%20networking%2C%20operating%20systems%20like%20Linux%2C%20programming%20languages%2C%20coding%20languages%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Muneeb%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717510127000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-21-1717502240.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352024%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Muneeb%20Amin%20Bhat%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20from%20Zungalpora%2C%20Kulgam%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20started%20by%20finding%20security%20breaches%20in%20his%20friends'%20and%20neighbours'%20computers.%20Today%2C%20he%20is%20doing%20this%20for%20over%2060%20international%20organisations%20including%20Apple%20and%20NASA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Grow%20a%20Vertical%20Vegetable%20Garden%20Using%20PVC%20Pipes%20On%20Your%20Terrace%20%26amp%3B%20Balcony%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOften%20those%20living%20in%20metropolitan%20cities%20hesitate%20to%20garden%20at%20home%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20space.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303431%2Fup-man-shows-how-to-grow-organic-vegetables-in-pvc-pipes-farming-startup-veg-roof%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMithilesh%20Kumar%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Sunita%20Prasad%20from%20Bihar%2C%20have%20defied%20this%20notion%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20urban%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mithilesh%20has%20successfully%20cultivated%20a%20variety%20of%20crops%20including%20chilli%2C%20coriander%2C%20tomato%2C%20brinjal%2C%20okra%2C%20peas%2C%20and%20bitter%20gourd%20in%20his%20compact%20garden%2C%20Sunita%20has%20also%20found%20similar%20success%20in%20her%20home%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20secret%3F%20Vertical%20gardening%20using%20PVC%20pipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20has%20installed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284723%2Fvertical-garden-pvc-pipes-bamboo-organic-vegetables-how-to-terrace-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPVC%20pipes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20create%20a%20vertical%20garden%20where%20she%20grows%20around%205%20kg%20of%20vegetables%20every%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mithilesh%20says%20that%20using%20PVC%20pipes%20saves%20space%20as%20well%20as%20money.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20general%2C%20PVC%20pipes%20are%20cheap%2C%20easy%20to%20find%2C%20and%20can%20save%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20does%20not%20require%20a%20complicated%20set%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sunita%20harvests%20at%20least%205%20kg%20of%20vegetables%20every%20week.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESunita%20harvests%20at%20least%205%20kg%20of%20vegetables%20every%20week.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ingenious%20gardeners%20share%20gardening%20tips%20for%20creating%20a%20vertical%20garden%20using%20PVC%20pipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.Take%20a%20five-foot%20pipe%20and%20cut%20it%20into%20sections%20according%20to%20the%20number%20of%20saplings%20or%20seeds%20you%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Avoid%20drilling%20an%20excessive%20number%20of%20holes%20in%20the%20pipe.%20Maintain%20a%20distance%20of%2018%20inches%20between%20holes%20on%20one%20side%20and%20a%20gap%20of%20nine%20inches%20on%20the%20opposite%20side%20of%20the%20pipe.%20In%20total%2C%20there%20should%20be%20five%20evenly%20spaced%20holes%20along%20a%20six-foot%20pipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Close%20the%20extra%20holes%2C%20if%20any%2C%20using%20a%20hot%20air%20gun.%20Do%20not%20forget%20to%20tape%20the%20extra%20holes%20to%20prevent%20water%20leakage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Fill%20three-fourth%20part%20of%20the%20pipe%20with%20soil%20and%20plant%20the%20seed%20or%20sapling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Add%20a%20mixture%20of%20vermicompost%20or%20any%20other%20organic%20fertiliser%20to%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Create%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20soil%20and%20fill%20it%20with%20sand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20Water%20the%20sand%20so%20that%20it%20stays%20wet%20and%20the%20moisture%20reaches%20the%20bottom%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20change%20the%20soil%20for%20the%20next%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20New%20saplings%20or%20seeds%20can%20be%20planted%20by%20simply%20making%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.%20Neem%20water%20can%20be%20used%20to%20avoid%20pests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGardening%20in%20two%20five-foot%20PVC%20pipes%20typically%20costs%20around%20Rs%201%2C000.%20With%20this%20setup%2C%20you%20can%20cultivate%20four%20to%20five%20varieties%20of%20vegetables%2C%20ranging%20from%20leafy%20greens%20to%20tubers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20gardening!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717507364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352038%2