0equal%20to%20using%202%2C500%20pads%20or%20tampons.%20Thirdly%2C%20effectiveness%3A%20One%20Asan%20Cup%20holds%20up%20to%20three%20times%20more%20than%20your%20average%20pad%2C%20so%20you%20can%20go%20up%20to%2012%20hours%20without%20changing%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNumber%20four%20is%20safety.%20Unlike%20pads%20and%20tampons%20which%20may%20contain%20undisclosed%20ingredients%2C%20the%20Asan%20cup%20is%20made%20of%20medical-grade%20silicone%2C%20certified%20safe%20for%20health.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20finally%20discretion%20and%20convenience.%20The%20compact%20size%20of%20the%20Asan%20cup%20ensures%20discreet%20use%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20maintain%20privacy%20about%20their%20menstrual%20cycle%2C%20avoiding%20the%20potential%20stigma%20associated%20with%20visible%20pads%20or%20cloth%20rags%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20to%20mention%20the%20reduction%20of%20sanitary%20pad%20waste%20which%20is%20reversed%20by%20the%20use%20of%20a%20menstrual%20cup%2C%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20reach%20rural%20women%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reach%20women%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20Asan%20also%20has%20a%20comprehensive%20behavioural%20change%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20programme%20to%20onboard%20and%20educate%20people%20on%20using%20the%20Asan%20Cup.%20The%20key%20to%20our%20behavioural%20change%20model%20is%20that%20education%20must%20come%20from%20a%20trusted%20source.%20For%20example%2C%20as%20someone%20from%20Bengaluru%20whose%20first%20language%20is%20English%2C%20I%20might%20not%20be%20a%20trusted%20source%20in%20a%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20we%20hired%20local%20social%20workers%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20use%20the%20cups%20themselves.%20They%20then%20trained%20rural%20women%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20cup%2C%20which%20eliminated%20s