E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20recipient%20receives%20a%20clutch%20storage%20pouch%2C%20a%20user%20manual%20in%20their%20local%20language%2C%20and%20a%20detailed%20educational%20session%20conducted%20by%20a%20local%20health%20worker.%20They%20also%20receive%20the%20health%20worker%E2%80%99s%20contact%20for%20follow-up%20sessions%20over%20the%20next%20six%20months.%20This%20comprehensive%20programme%20ensures%20that%20everyone%20has%20the%20resources%20and%20support%20needed%20to%20safely%20use%20the%20Asan%20Cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20she%20has%20reached%20out%20to%2015%2C000%20women%20in%2060%20villages%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Kanakapura.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20single%20woman%20in%20those%20areas%20are%20using%20the%20Asan%20cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagamma%2C%2036%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Kanakapura%2C%20complained%20that%20she%20can%E2%80%99t%20wear%20her%20favourite%20white%20sarees%20fearing%20stains%20during%20her%20periods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20have%20been%20using%20the%20Asan%20cup%20for%20several%20months%20now%20and%20the%20scenario%20has%20changed.%20The%20line%20between%20the%20period%20and%20non-period%20days%20has%20blurred.%20I%20have%20recommended%20it%20to%20my%20niece%20now%20as%20well.%20The%20pads%20used%20to%20give%20me%20rashes%20on%20the%20thighs%20but%20now%20there%20are%20no%20such%20issues.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20I%20wear%20whatever%20colour%20saree%20I%20want%20without%20any%20fear%20of%20stains%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayalakshmi%2C%2038%2C%20highlighted%20that%20she%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321703%2Fiit-material-scientists-innovate-biodegradable-super-absorbent-sheets-for-sanitary-pads%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%20the%20used%20pads%20in%20a%20plastic%20bag%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20burn%20them.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20other%20choice%2C%20I%20just%20burned%20them%20when%20no%20one%20was%20watching.%20But%20not%20with%20the%20Asan%20cup%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20that.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20used%20to%20hate%20travelling%20to%20work%20while%20wearing%20a%20pad%20in%20the%20heat%20but%20now%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20any%20discomfort%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Asan%20continuously%20reaches%20women%20in%20rural%20India%2C%20Ira%20believes%20that%20her%20work%20is%20not%20over.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20still%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20women%20using%20rags%20and%20lacking%20any%20access%20to%20menstrual%20hygiene.%20If%20even%20one%20woman%20is%20without%20access%20to%20menstrual%20hygiene%2C%20my%20job%20is%20not%20over.%20As%20a%20company%2C%20we%20want%20to%20eradicate%20period%20poverty%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Ira%20Guha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717079206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-1-1717078112.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cups%20come%20with%20a%20cloth%20bag%20and%20a%20instruction%20manual%20in%20the%20local%20language.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351606%2Fmenstrual-cups-made-in-india-asan-cup-how-to-use-ira-guha-period-hygiene-for-rural-women-karnataka%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Organic%20Tea%20Tasting%20%26amp%3B%20Waterfall%20Picnics%3A%20Eco-Stay%20in%20Coonoor%20Is%20a%20Nature%20Lover%E2%80%99s%20Dream%20Destination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20her%2010th%20birthday%2C%20Mahima%20Sukhdev%E2%80%99s%20parents%20Vinati%20and%20Pavan%20posed%20a%20very%20important%20question%20to%20her%3A%20How%20would%20you%20like%20to%20celebrate%3F%20They%20had%20imagined%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20coloured%20responses%20%E2%80%94%20think%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20a%20little%20girl%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20fantasies%20%E2%80%94%20and%20weren%E2%80%99t%20prepared%20for%20the%20ask%20to%20be%20a%20trip%20to%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Borivali%20National%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325308%2Frare-wildlife-conservation-photos-from-across-the-world-nature-infocus-kalyan-varma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeep%20love%20for%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vinati%20reminisces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20humoured%20by%20their%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20request%2C%20the%20couple%20went%20ahead%20and%20planned%20the%20nature%20trip.%20That%20day%2C%20Mahima%E2%80%99s%20friends%20returned%20home%20with%20beautiful%20return%20gifts%20%E2%80%94%20books%20that%20spoke%20of%20the%20birds%20and%20fauna%20at%20the%20national%20park.%20As%20Mahima%20grew%20older%2C%20her%20fascination%20for%20the%20outdoors%20only%20deepened.%20And%20whether%20it%20was%20nature%20trails%2C%20hikes%2C%20trips%20to%20safaris%20or%20afternoon%20picnics%2C%20her%20parents%20would%20always%20oblige.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelling%20these%20stories%20gets%20Vinati%20chuckling.%20After%20all%2C%20she%20sees%20them%20as%20jigsaw%20pieces%20that%20played%20a%20role%20in%20fortifying%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20nature.%20She%20says%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20Mahima%E2%80%99s%20passion%20rubbed%20off%20on%20her%2C%20her%20husband%2C%20and%20their%20daughter%20Ashima%2C%20and%20they%20grew%20as%20intrigued%20by%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinati%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20based%20in%20London%2C%20sees%20those%20years%20of%20innocence%20as%20the%20fabric%20that%20wove%20together%20the%20story%20of%20O%E2%8