E2%80%94%20including%20Australia%2C%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Dubai%2C%20Germany%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Brazil.%20Today%2C%20the%20startup%E2%80%99s%20annual%20revenue%20stands%20at%20Rs%201.5%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmploying%20rural%20households%20with%20dignity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20five%20flavours%20%E2%80%94%20garlic%20green%20chilli%2C%20garlic%20red%20chilli%2C%20garlic%20yellow%20chilli%2C%20hemp%2C%20and%20mint%20%E2%80%94%20today%20HimFla%20has%2052%20flavours.%20These%20include%20%3Cem%3Etimur%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Szechuan%20pepper%20harvested%20from%20the%20higher%20Himalayan%20regions%20of%20Uttarakhand)%20and%20hemp%2C%20which%20is%20a%20rich%20source%20of%20omega%2C%20Gandreni%20%3Cem%3Ekala%20jeera%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20cumin)%2C%20and%20many%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20sources%20pink%20rock%20salt%20from%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20spices%20and%20herbs%20from%201%2C000%20small%20farmers%20from%20100%20villages%20across%20Nainital%2C%20Bageshwar%2C%20Chamoli%2C%20and%20Almora.%20With%20this%20work%2C%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20financially%20empower%2080%20rural%20women%20who%20have%20dropped%20shovels%20to%20grind%20spices%20and%20herbs%20on%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1716968106.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Every%20month%2C%20HimFla%20manufactures%20up%20to%2020%20quintals%20of%20flavoured%20salt.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1716968106.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1716968106-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1